.Dt NHI 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm nhi
.Nd USB4 host interface
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "nhi* at pci?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the USB4 host interface.
.Pp
The driver does not implement any meaningful USB4 connection manager
functionality.
It only puts the router that is part of the host interface into a sleep state
during suspend.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4 ,
.Xr xhci 4
